---
<section class="subscribe-frame reveal" id="subscribe" aria-labelledby="subscribe-title">
  <div class="subscribe-inner">
    <h2 id="subscribe-title">Walk the Yes-Way.</h2>
    <p>A letter for people building strength, choosing responsibility, and putting their work in service of something larger.</p>
    <form class="subscribe-form" action="https://josephiesue.com/join" method="get">
      <label class="sr-only" for="email">Email address</label>
      <input id="email" name="email" type="email" autocomplete="email" placeholder="Email address" />
      <button type="submit">Join the letter <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></button>
    </form>
    <a class="rss-link" href="/rss.xml">Prefer RSS?</a>
  </div>
</section>
